title: Sherlock Holmes and the Case of the Silk Stocking.zip
description:
This is a rip of Sherlock Holmes and the Case of the Silk Stocking. I ripped this with Handbrake into an AVI. I\&#039;ll keep seeding this day and night, so there\&#039;s always going to be at least one seed on it.

Great movie. Personally, the quality on this isn\&#039;t DVD quality, but it\&#039;s fine for a viewing. I own the DVD, so I ripped it from that. If something\&#039;s wrong, don\&#039;t hesitate to comment here about it and I\&#039;ll try and fix it as soon as possible.

Just figured I\&#039;d give back to the community after taking so much.
